1) Define your mission,

31
00:02:04,801 --> 00:02:11,629
2)Define and engage your stakeholders,
3) Assess existing alternatives

32
00:02:08,001 --> 00:02:11,001


33
00:02:11,829 --> 00:02:14,915
and competition and understand
why they are falling short,

34
00:02:15,115 --> 00:02:20,939
4) Define the specification or specs of
the solution you have identified.

35
00:02:22,059 --> 00:02:25,001
Naturally, the first task for you
is to define your mission,

36
00:02:25,201 --> 00:02:28,419
in other words: What problem
are you trying to solve, 

37
00:02:28,619 --> 00:02:30,999
and what change do
you want to achieve?

38
00:02:31,721 --> 00:02:33,747
After you have done that,
then you need to go back 

