00:02:51,573 --> 00:02:55,471
 you wish to propose
to address the problem,

44
00:02:55,671 --> 00:02:59,853
with a view to achieving your
desired change in the long term.

45
00:03:02,096 --> 00:03:05,252
Then, after that, you need
to understand and define

46
00:03:05,452 --> 00:03:08,447
who your stakeholders are exactly,

