Afterwards, create a Stakeholders'
Rating Table and identify

51
00:03:29,894 --> 00:03:32,306
 the ones who are absolutely key,
for example,

52
00:03:32,506 --> 00:03:37,172
those scoring high on interest
and power to affect your solution.

