00:03:38,131 --> 00:03:42,229
But also identify those capable
of influencing perceptions 

54
00:03:42,429 --> 00:03:46,942
and opinion on your solution,
that is the Key Opinion Leaders.

55
00:03:47,834 --> 00:03:52,010
Engage them as extensively
as feasible, in order to understand

56
00:03:52,210 --> 00:03:56,166
what type of solution they
really wish to see for this problem.

57
00:03:56,366 --> 00:04:02,890
Now, discuss your proposed solution
and find out what their opinion is

58
00:04:03,090 --> 00:04:05,885
 and what feedback
they can give you on it.

